{"ts":"2026-07-21T19:52:47.907Z","author":"codex-jellyfin","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-21T19:52:47.907Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-21T19:52:47.903Z","author":"codex-jellyfin","text":"Current quality evidence: typecheck and strict ESLint pass; every source file is at or below 300 code lines excluding comments; tracked-tree and repository-history secret scans pass. jscpd reports a 5.78% duplicated-line baseline, so zero-duplication and the complete mandatory gate bundle remain open work."}]}],"before_hash":"671bb93991a63a255d599000a5f5b7382dee1c07e94dade74ca1849dfb4fa36e","after_hash":"c9693604ef65ae031ecf32655f3eada594627a1ea33c20e68200f4d80b57a2b1"}
{"ts":"2026-07-21T20:04:31.266Z","author":"codex-jellyfin","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/1","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-21T20:04:31.266Z","author":"codex-jellyfin","text":"Strict TypeScript and JSDoc lint, source LOC, and both secret scans pass. The zero-duplication command is now explicit as check:duplicates, but remains red at the measured 5.78% baseline and is intentionally not represented as a completed release gate."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-21T20:04:31.266Z"}],"before_hash":"c9693604ef65ae031ecf32655f3eada594627a1ea33c20e68200f4d80b57a2b1","after_hash":"af16bf42c638a024e85de96fdf83b8ff7107a1e10b060c8eae15456924f52561"}
{"ts":"2026-07-21T20:09:41.950Z","author":"codex-jellyfin","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/2","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-21T20:09:41.945Z","author":"codex-jellyfin","text":"Dependency remediation completed for the current lane: compatible overrides pin vite 8.1.5, flatted 3.4.2, postcss 8.5.21, esbuild 0.28.1, and picomatch 4.0.5; both bun audit and npm audit now report zero vulnerabilities. Typecheck, lint, and all 903 non-live tests still pass."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-21T20:09:41.950Z"}],"before_hash":"af16bf42c638a024e85de96fdf83b8ff7107a1e10b060c8eae15456924f52561","after_hash":"afcefef9c2f7b17c18795db424e6bc337f4546545125e2a5fbdd02db11627e8c"}
